      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WESTERN LIES (1) is a talented type and proved too classy last time to win by 2.25 lengths at this track in a handy 16.77 beating PAW UNTIL PAYDAY. Winner at his latest appearance in the quickest time on the card. Well placed and will be tough to beat. SWIFT GRANT (8) has an impressive record and comes into this as a quickest on the card winner last time at this track, scoring by 1.3 lengths (23.31). Solid record at the distance winning six races. Form from his last run is proving to be solid. One of main contenders. HANNAH GOANNA (6) shapes well for this on her quick win a few runs back, getting around Grafton over 350m in 19.97 then hitting the frame in both runs since. Expecting another bold showing. BIG BUCKETS (7) is always hard to beat when he races at this trip.",
